# PATCH: 0034-repo-file-browser
# WHY: O script filename user phai go tay ten file, khong biet repo co gi. Can duyet cay thu muc git
#      de chon file, va tao moi thu muc / file ngay do.
# WHAT: Backend hook mong ListTemplateRepoDir + route GET /gitea/dir (logic ListDir o giteamanager).
#       TemplateForm.vue: nut Browse + dialog duyet (folder/file, len cap, chon file), nut New folder
#       (tao <dir>/.gitkeep) + New file (mo editor 0029 tai thu muc hien tai). +i18n scriptBrowse*.
# SPEC: docs/L2-specs/core-patches/0034-repo-file-browser.md
# BASELINE: v2.18.16
#
